  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chopped garlic and sauté for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add chopped chives and cook for an additional minute, until slightly softened.",
    "Add pressure-cooked potatoes and mash with a fork until they reach the desired consistency.",
    "Add unsalted butter and stir until melted.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the hash to a serving dish and garnish with chopped fresh parsley and a squeeze of lemon juice.",
    "Serve hot."
